nodes.text: During the Clone Wars, Jedi Master Kit Fisto was in command of a fleet following the rescue of Viceroy Nute Gunray by Separatist agents. In the aftermath of the rescue, Jedi General Luminara Unduli and Jedi Padawan Ahsoka Tano reported to Master Yoda and Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker that Fisto's fleet was near Gunray's position.
